msgid "0:[name]梢[line]「この剣が、怖くて、仕方なかった」[%p]"
msgstr "0:[name]梢[line]I used to think this sword was so scary...[%p]"

msgid "100:折原梢は、東京に出てくるまで、そう思っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "100:That's what she'd thought until she came to Tokyo.[%p]"

msgid "200:だが、今は違う。[linebreak]今では、彼女にとってとても大切で、かけがえのないものとなった。[%p]"
msgstr "200:But now she felt differently. Now, it was something precious, something very important to her.[%p]"

msgid "300:この剣があれば、怖くない。[linebreak]この剣が、自分を守ってくれる。[linebreak]この剣は、自分の心。もうひとりの、自分。[%p]"
msgstr "300:As long as she had the sword, there was nothing to be scared of. The sword would protect her. The sword was her heart. It was her other self.[%p]"

msgid "400:そう思うようになったのは、もう３週間ほども前――[%p]"
msgstr "400:It was about three weeks ago that she'd changed her mind.[%p]"

msgid "500:梢には、幼い頃から、他人の心の声が聞こえてしまうという力があった。[%p]"
msgstr "500:Kozue had always had the power to hear what other people were thinking.[%p]"

msgid "600:それをいつ自覚するようになったのかは、もう覚えていない。[%p]"
msgstr "600:She couldn't remember anymore when she'd first realized she had it.[%p]"

msgid "700:自分がおかしくなったんだ、病気になっちゃったんだ――[linebreak]梢は幼いながらに、この力は誰にも悟られちゃいけないものなんだと思った。[%p]"
msgstr "700:She'd thought she'd gone crazy, or that she was sick. In her own, childish way, she'd thought that she couldn't let anybody find out.[%p]"

msgid "800:だから、両親にも隠していた。[%p]"
msgstr "800:She hadn't told anybody, not even her parents.[%p]"

msgid "900:力のせいで友人もできず、家族とも溝ができ、“やたらと勘のいい子”と周囲から気味悪がられた。[%p]"
msgstr "900:Because of her power, she couldn't make any friends. It created a rift between her and her family, too. All the people around her started to think she was creepy, that her intuition was “a little too good.”[%p]"

msgid "1000:渋谷に来ても、彼女は学校へ行くことが怖かった。誰とも会いたくなかった。どうせまた気味悪がられるに決まってると考えていた。[%p]"
msgstr "1000:Even after coming to Shibuya, she'd been scared to go to school. She hadn't wanted to talk to anybody. She'd thought they'd just find her creepy again.[%p]"

msgid "1100:本来転入するはずだった日も、その次の日も、さらに次の日も、学校へ行かずに朝から渋谷の街をさまよい歩いていた。[%p]"
msgstr "1100:The first day she was supposed to go to school, and the day after that, and even the day after that, she'd skipped school and spent the day wandering around Shibuya instead.[%p]"

msgid "1200:きっと両親には学校から連絡が行っていただろう。梢が無断欠席していることには気付いたはずだ。でも２人は梢になにも言ってこなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "1200:She knew the school must have contacted her parents. They must've known Kozue wasn't going. But the two of them didn't say anything to her at all.[%p]"

msgid "1300:中学生と間違われてもおかしくない容姿の梢が平日の午前中から街を歩いていても、彼女が以前住んでいた田舎とは違って、咎める人間はひとりもいなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "1300:Kozue looked young enough to be mistaken for a middle schooler, and yet unlike back home in the countryside, nobody stopped her when she was out in the middle of the day.[%p]"

msgid "1400:渋谷を徘徊するようになって数日。[%p]"
msgstr "1400:She'd spent days wandering around Shibuya.[%p]"

msgid "1500:Ｒｏｆｔ内の階段という、彼女にとっての憩いの場所を見つけ、そこに座り込んでぼんやりするのが日課になった。[%p]"
msgstr "1500:She'd found her little peaceful spot in the Roft stairwell, and every day she'd go up there to sit.[%p]"

msgid "1600:その日も、夕方になるまで４時間近くもそこで過ごした後、帰ろうとＲｏｆｔを出た。[%p]"
msgstr "1600:One day, she'd spent almost four hours there, until the sun finally began to set. Then she'd left Roft to go home.[%p]"

msgid "1700:鈍色の空からは雨の雫が落ちてきていた。[%p]"
msgstr "1700:Raindrops were pouring from the dull gray sky.[%p]"

msgid "1800:梢は傘を持っていなかったが、空を見上げることもなく、濡れることも気にせず、力のない足取りで雨の中へと足を踏み出した。[%p]"
msgstr "1800:She hadn't brought an umbrella, but she neither looked up at the sky nor seemed to care about getting wet. She simply headed home through the rain on unsteady feet.[%p]"

msgid "1900:そこで、ふと彼女の視界に飛び込んできたもの。[%p]"
msgstr "1900:Then she saw something in the corner of her eye.[%p]"

msgid "2000:“世界は終わる”[%p]"
msgstr "2000:It was a sign that read, “The End Is Near.”[%p]"

msgid "2100:そう書かれたボード。[linebreak]雨に濡れ、手書きの字はにじんでしまっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "2100:The hand-written text was blurring in the rain.[%p]"

msgid "2200:そのボードを持っていたのは、ひとりのホームレスの男で、こんな雨の中、道端に気配を消して座り込んでいた。[%p]"
msgstr "2200:Holding the board was a homeless man, sitting unobtrusively on the side of the road in the middle of the pouring rain.[%p]"

msgid "2300:うなだれ、その表情は見えない。もしかしたら、死んでいるのかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "2300:His head was slumped forward, and she couldn't see his expression. He might've been dead.[%p]"

msgid "2400:その姿が――[%p]"
msgstr "2400:The way he looked...[%p]"

msgid "2500:さっきまでＲｏｆｔの階段にいた自分とだぶって、梢は足を止めていた。[%p]"
msgstr "2500:reminded her of how she'd looked sitting in the Roft stairwell. She stopped.[%p]"

msgid "2600:[name]梢[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "2600:[name]梢[line]...[%p]"

msgid "2700:少しの間、躊躇した。[%p]"
msgstr "2700:For a moment, she hesitated.[%p]"

msgid "2800:見ず知らずの、しかも東京に来る前には見たことがなかったホームレス。その姿に嫌悪感すら覚えた。もしここで話しかけて、恐ろしいことに巻き込まれたらどうしよう……そんな不安。[%p]"
msgstr "2800:She'd never met this man, and had never even seen a homeless person until she came to Tokyo. He looked repulsive. She was scared that if she talked to him, something horrible might happen to her.[%p]"

msgid "2900:けれどそのときの梢は、その不安以上に、男を殺してやりたいという衝動が強かった。あまりにも唐突な衝動だったが、そうすることで今の自分も殺せるんじゃないかという気がした。[%p]"
msgstr "2900:But there was another desire that won out over her fear, a desire to kill him. It was such a sudden, strong impulse that she thought that if she obeyed it, she might be able to kill herself, too.[%p]"

msgid "3000:だから迷った末に、男に“心の声”を送っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "3000:So, after a short moment's hesitation, she spoke to him with the voice in her mind.[%p]"

msgid "3100:[name]梢[line]「世界は、終わるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "3100:[name]梢[line]Is the world going to end?[%p]"

msgid "3200:男の肩が、ピクリと震える。[linebreak]死んでいたわけではなかった。[linebreak]ゆっくりと、顔を上げる。[%p]"
msgstr "3200:Suddenly his shoulders twitched. He wasn't dead after all. He slowly raised his head.[%p]"

msgid "3300:濡れた前髪の間からのぞく濁った目が、梢を見上げてきた。[%p]"
msgstr "3300:His cloudy eyes peered through his soaked hair as he looked up at her.[%p]"

msgid "3400:[name]男[line]「ああ。終わるよ」[%p]"
msgstr "3400:[name]男[line]Yeah. It's going to end.[%p]"

msgid "3500:梢は驚き、わずかに目を見開いた。[%p]"
msgstr "3500:Kozue's eyes went a little wide with surprise.[%p]"

msgid "3600:世界が終わると言い切ったことにではなく。[linebreak]男が、返事をしたことに対して。[%p]"
msgstr "3600:Not at being told that the world would end. But at the fact that the man had replied to her.[%p]"

msgid "3700:返事なんて期待していなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "3700:She hadn't expected a reply.[%p]"

msgid "3800:心の声を送られた相手は、戸惑って幻聴かと思い込もうとするか、恐怖に震えてその場を足早に立ち去るかのどちらかだ。[%p]"
msgstr "3800:Most people she spoke to like this either tried to convince themselves they were hearing things, or got scared and quickly left.[%p]"

msgid "3900:もしコミュニケーションに成功したとしても、ここまで整然と返事をよこしてくるのは難しいこと。[%p]"
msgstr "3900:Even if she did succeed in communicating with somebody, it was hard for them to send back such a straightforward, understandable reply.[%p]"

msgid "4000:人の思考というものは、あまりにも脈絡がなく無秩序だから。[%p]"
msgstr "4000:Doing so was difficult. Human thought was disordered and random.[%p]"

msgid "4100:なのに男は、表情をなんら変えず。[linebreak]梢の問いかけに、シンプルに一言だけで答えてきたのだ。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:But the man hadn't seemed surprised at all. Instead, he'd given her a short, simple answer.[%p]"

msgid "4200:男の声を通して感じる心には、深い悲しみが満ちていた。心が、泣いていた。梢にはそう思えた。[%p]"
msgstr "4200:Through his voice, she could feel a deep sadness filling his heart. His heart was crying. That's how it felt to her.[%p]"

msgid "4300:[name]男[line]「君は、剣を持っているね？」[%p]"
msgstr "4300:[name]男[line]You have a sword, don't you?[%p]"

msgid "4400:[name]梢[line]「どうして分かるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "4400:[name]梢[line]How do you know?[%p]"

msgid "4500:[name]男[line]「君のような子を、他にも知っているから」[%p]"
msgstr "4500:[name]男[line]I know other children like you.[%p]"

msgid "4600:梢は頭上に手を掲げ、その場でディソードを取り出して見せた。男に切っ先を突きつける。[%p]"
msgstr "4600:She put her hand above her head and summoned her Di-Sword. She pointed the blade at him.[%p]"

msgid "4700:[name]梢[line]「この剣が、見えるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "4700:[name]梢[line]Can you see this sword?[%p]"

msgid "4800:[name]男[line]「見えないよ」[%p]"
msgstr "4800:[name]男[line]I can't.[%p]"

msgid "4900:[name]梢[line]「じゃあ、どうして分かるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "4900:[name]梢[line]Then how do you know?[%p]"

msgid "5000:[name]男[line]「おじさんが、悪い人だからだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "5000:[name]男[line]Because I'm a bad man.[%p]"

msgid "5100:[name]男[line]「……済まない」[%p]"
msgstr "5100:[name]男[line]I'm sorry.[%p]"

msgid "5200:[name]梢[line]「どうして、謝るの？」[%p]"
msgstr "5200:[name]梢[line]Why are you apologizing?[%p]"

msgid "5300:[name]男[line]「おじさんの、せいなんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "5300:[name]男[line]It's my fault.[%p]"

msgid "5400:[name]梢[line]「どうして、おじさんのせいなの？」[%p]"
msgstr "5400:[name]梢[line]Why is it your fault?[%p]"

msgid "5500:[name]男[line]「忠告しかできないから」[%p]"
msgstr "5500:[name]男[line]Because all I can do is warn others.[%p]"

msgid "5600:[name]男[line]「動き出してしまったから」[%p]"
msgstr "5600:[name]男[line]Because it's started.[%p]"

msgid "5700:[name]男[line]「もう、おじさんには止める術がないから」[%p]"
msgstr "5700:[name]男[line]Because there's nothing I can do to stop it.[%p]"

msgid "5800:[name]梢[line]「じゃあ、おじさんを殺せば、こずぴぃは悪くなくなるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "5800:[name]梢[line]So, if Kozupii kills you, does that mean she won't be bad anymore?[%p]"

msgid "5900:[name]男[line]「その剣は、君を殺すものにも、守るものにもなる」[%p]"
msgstr "5900:[name]男[line]That sword can kill you, and it can protect you.[%p]"

msgid "6000:[name]男[line]「思い出してごらん？」[%p]"
msgstr "6000:[name]男[line]Try to remember.[%p]"

msgid "6100:[name]男[line]「空を見れば雲が」[%p]"
msgstr "6100:[name]男[line]When you look up the sky, you see the clouds.[%p]"

msgid "6200:[name]男[line]「川を見れば流れが」[%p]"
msgstr "6200:[name]男[line]When you look at the river, you see the flow of the water.[%p]"

msgid "6300:[name]男[line]「そこにあったはず」[%p]"
msgstr "6300:[name]男[line]They're always there.[%p]"

msgid "6400:[name]男[line]「それと同じこと」[%p]"
msgstr "6400:[name]男[line]This is the same.[%p]"

msgid "6500:[name]男[line]「その剣はいつも君のそばにあった」[%p]"
msgstr "6500:[name]男[line]The sword was always with you.[%p]"

msgid "6600:[name]男[line]「自分自身の心を見てごらん」[%p]"
msgstr "6600:[name]男[line]Look into your heart.[%p]"

msgid "6700:[name]男[line]「そこにあるのが、その剣なんだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "6700:[name]男[line]The sword is what you'll find there.[%p]"

msgid "6800:[name]梢[line]「でも、殺したいって願ったら、これが手許にあったんだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "6800:[name]梢[line]But it came to me when I wished to kill.[%p]"

msgid "6900:[name]梢[line]「この剣は、こずぴぃと、こずぴぃの周囲にあるあらゆるものを殺すためのものじゃないの？」[%p]"
msgstr "6900:[name]梢[line]Isn't this sword supposed to kill me, and all the people around me?[%p]"

msgid "7000:[name]男[line]「負の感情は、否定されるものじゃない」[%p]"
msgstr "7000:[name]男[line]It's wrong to deny your negative feelings.[%p]"

msgid "7100:[name]男[line]「人が誰しも持つものだからね」[%p]"
msgstr "7100:[name]男[line]Every person has them.[%p]"

msgid "7200:[name]男[line]「特別じゃないんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "7200:[name]男[line]You're not special.[%p]"

msgid "7300:[name]男[line]「どう向き合うか、だよ」[%p]"
msgstr "7300:[name]男[line]It's how you choose to face them.[%p]"

msgid "7400:[name]男[line]「目をそらしてはいけない」[%p]"
msgstr "7400:[name]男[line]You can't look away.[%p]"

msgid "7500:[name]男[line]「自分を、否定してはいけない」[%p]"
msgstr "7500:[name]男[line]You can't deny who you are.[%p]"

msgid "7600:[name]男[line]「世界は、鏡像」[%p]"
msgstr "7600:[name]男[line]The world is a reflection in a mirror.[%p]"

msgid "7700:[name]男[line]「君の心の中にある正は」[%p]"
msgstr "7700:[name]男[line]What's positive in your heart,[%p]"

msgid "7800:[name]男[line]「同時に負となり得るし」[%p]"
msgstr "7800:[name]男[line]may also be negative.[%p]"

msgid "7900:[name]男[line]「その逆もまた、可能」[%p]"
msgstr "7900:[name]男[line]And the opposite is true, too.[%p]"

msgid "8000:[name]男[line]「世界が終わるのか、生き続けるのか、それを選べるのは……」[%p]"
msgstr "8000:[name]男[line]Whether the world ends, or continues to live on...[%p]"

msgid "8100:[name]男[line]「君たちだけなんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "8100:[name]男[line]It's up to you children to decide.[%p]"

msgid "8200:結局、梢は男を殺さなかった。衝動は、話しているうちにいつの間にか霧散していた。[%p]"
msgstr "8200:In the end, she hadn't killed the man. The desire to do so receded as they spoke.[%p]"

msgid "8300:男の言葉の意味はよく分からなかった。[linebreak]それでも、必死に考えて、やがて梢はひとつの結論に至った。[%p]"
msgstr "8300:She didn't understand what the man was trying to say. But she thought and thought, as hard as she could, and finally reached a conclusion.[%p]"

msgid "8400:この剣は、自分。[linebreak]否定せずに見れば。[linebreak]自分を助けてくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "8400:The sword was her. She'd looked at it without denying it, and it had saved her.[%p]"

msgid "8500:だから梢は、純粋な気持ちで、[linebreak]この剣に、依存する。[%p]"
msgstr "8500:That's why she'd come to depend on it, in her own pure-hearted way.[%p]"

